import http from './http'

export let urlPrefix = '/oa'

// export const articleList = (data) => http(`${urlPrefix}/articleList`, data, 'POST') // 查询文章列表

export const articleList = (data) => http(`http://localhost:8181/book/findAll/${data.current}/${data.size}`, data, 'GET') // 查询文章列表
export const articleSave = (data) => http(`http://localhost:8181/book/save`, data, 'POST') // 新增文章列表
